label.value: adult multiglomerular antennal lobe projection neuron type 86 vPN

value.value: Adult multiglomerular antennal lobe projection neuron belonging to group 86 (Scheffer et al., 2020). It develops from neuroblast ALv1 and follows the mediolateral antennal lobe tract (Bates et al., 2020; Scheffer et al., 2020). It has postsynaptic sites in the lateral horn, antennal lobe and antennal lobe glomerulus DC4 (Scheffer et al., 2020). It has presynaptic sites in the lateral horn (Scheffer et al., 2020).

definition.value: Uncharacterized putative cell type (based on clustering analysis) from Janelia hemibrain data (Scheffer et al., 2020). Connectivity based on Hemibrain v1.1 data where each individual of this type has at least 10 synapses in a region.
